data.description: This refreshed Rough River refuge is the way to own lakefront property at an affordable price. This Mobile Home has been converted to real property. The Sellers are only the second owners of the 1996 Horton Mirage so it was kept well, but still recently updated for you to enjoy! The owners say that a dock should be possible with COE approval and the easy path through the back yard will get you there. The home offers 2 bedrooms, 1 full bathroom, laundry, open living & kitchen, as well as a nice back deck, fire pit, storage shed, driveway, plus additional parking spaces at the road. It's clean and turn key, everything that leads to you enjoying right away!
